    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >~~ 主线剧情 ~~</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/009c7c18d5f2f13046b1df588d036ef8.poster.avif?t=1703141629\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/009c7c18d5f2f13046b1df588d036ef8.webm?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/009c7c18d5f2f13046b1df588d036ef8.mp4?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>第莫西的祖父因诅咒而亡……<br>悲痛之余，第莫西忽然想起了曾听闻过的“姆之塔”的传说。<br>传说姆之塔是一座神所建立的塔，它高耸入云，只要能登上塔顶，就能实现任何愿望。<br>然而，这是一座潜伏着数不尽的魔物和机关暗器的恐怖之塔，已经葬送了无数挑战者的生命。<br>究竟第莫西能否平安爬上高塔，又能否实现让祖父复活的愿望呢……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >~~游戏特色~~</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/d0bf61017e0c9cff17fefe642a40005d.poster.avif?t=1703141629\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/d0bf61017e0c9cff17fefe642a40005d.webm?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/d0bf61017e0c9cff17fefe642a40005d.mp4?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>第莫西的本领是弹弓攻击、跳跃和冲刺。<br>想爬上高塔，就必须要靠这三种本领来破解越来越多的魔物和困难重重的陷阱。<br>为此，精准的移动操作是不可或缺的。<br>好好磨练对跳跃高度、冲刺距离、以及操作时机的把控，让第莫西得心应手地行动，朝着塔顶进发吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/582b4ddbd1ed63b09628c193f7965742.poster.avif?t=1703141629\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/582b4ddbd1ed63b09628c193f7965742.webm?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/582b4ddbd1ed63b09628c193f7965742.mp4?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在这场冒险中，第莫西必须面对10个BOSS敌人。不论哪个估计都将会是一场恶战……<br>除了磨炼自己的精神、专注力、操作技术之外，你别无他法。靠死亡来积累经验，再度发起挑战吧!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/f670f929bd14331a694b04e7936429f2.poster.avif?t=1703141629\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/f670f929bd14331a694b04e7936429f2.webm?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/f670f929bd14331a694b04e7936429f2.mp4?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>本作由5个迷宫构成，它们有着各异的主题风格以及攻略方法。<br>你需要穿过植物的包围，避开回旋的利刃、躲闪袭来的子弹……<br>当然，阻挡在第莫西前方的魔物，也是多种多样千奇百怪。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/3fd622cf8aae0217c0126ac3e5983e62.poster.avif?t=1703141629\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/3fd622cf8aae0217c0126ac3e5983e62.webm?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/3fd622cf8aae0217c0126ac3e5983e62.mp4?t=1703141629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>姆之塔里栖息着超过50种的魔物。<br>冒险越往后，魔物也就会变得越难对付，必须多多磨练，用最少的损伤来攻克难关。<br><br><br><strong><i>游戏系统</i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>硬核动作要素<br></li><li>超过50种敌人 <br></li><li>高难度BOSS战 <br></li><li>风格迥异的5大迷宫 <br></li><li>RPG元素、解谜元素、料理等任务 <br></li><li>隐藏在世界中的多个秘密 <br></li><li>芯片音乐风格BGM<br></li><li>红白机游戏的进化型</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/2d1636b7e758bf8885fcc430bcb98db1.apng?t=1703141629\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695260/extras/2d1636b7e758bf8885fcc430bcb98db1.poster.avif?t=1703141629\" class=\"bb_img\" width=90 height=131 /></picture></span>",
